===Barracuda Webfilter Technology Add-on===

   Author: Aplura, LLC

   Version/Date: 20120316

   Supported product(s): The product(s) that the Technology Add-on supports, including
   which version(s) you know it supports

   Source type(s): The list of source types the Technology Add-on handles

   Input requirements: This TA will read a syslog feed and find the http_scan events.
	These are index-time transforms. The incoming "syslog" sourcetype events are
	then changes to "barracuda:web_filter"

